  <div class="p-4 p-md-5 mb-4 rounded text-body-emphasis bg-body-secondary">
    <div class="col-lg-6 px-0">
      <h1 class="display-4 fst-italic">SHAWN'S WATCH HISTORY</h1>
      <p class="lead my-3">Sometimes I watch shows and then I'll forget... So this website will record the things I watch,
        whether it be a Netflix show, movie, anime or K-Drama, and I'll document my feelings towards them. Now I can
        have confidence in my recommendations!

        Sorted with my top recommendations up top. Sort by title, newest, or best.</p>
    </div>
